{"tid":2426743,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Bill Gates首次玩Clubhouse爆料.  不愛蘋果愛Android 不是比特幣粉絲","createTime":"2021-02-28T10:03:37.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-02T18:57:46.000Z","uid":105678,"like":7,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"6c6df28afd45d8f444078bb948ec65a68a8f02fe","tid":2426743,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T10:03:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/maxresdefault-4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F02%2Fmaxresdefault-4.jpg&h=2c073b1f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n微軟創辦人蓋茨( Bill Gates）近日出新書《如何避免氣候災難》(How to Avoid a Climate Disaster) ，並首次加入音頻社交網絡Clubhouse接受記者安德魯&middot;羅斯&middot;索爾金（Andrew Ross Sorkin）的專訪，爆料指自己並未使用蘋果手機，又指比特幣消耗大量的能源並不環保，明確表明自己不是比特幣的粉絲。<br />\n<br />\n蓋茨表示自己並未使用蘋果手機，他認為Android 手機預裝了Microsoft軟件，用起來很方便，在軟件與操作系統的連接方式上更加靈活，指自己已經習慣Android，但知道有很多朋友都在使用iPhone。<br />\n<br />\n另外蓋茨指，比特幣每筆交易及掘礦消耗大量的電量並不環保，挖掘加密貨幣需要大量的計算能力和能源消耗，並明確表明自己不是比特幣的粉絲，蓋茨指「我沒有選擇投資比特幣，而是將資金用於購買瘧疾疫苗。我投資於生產真正產品的公司。但如果其他人投資比特幣並發了財，我會祝賀他們。」<br />\n<br />\n蓋茨不久前第二次接受了疫苗接種，他表示想作為防疫的好榜樣，指自己亦會繼續戴口罩，又表示最近迷上了Netflix的法國懸疑驚悚片《亞森-羅賓》(Lupin)。<br />\n<br />\n資料來源 : GeekWire<br />\n<br />\n連標基都覺得iphone唔方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b50f69fbda9fb685206af75e534e2689d14c2e2","tid":2426743,"uid":74728,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T10:15:01.000Z","msg":"他認為Android 手機預裝了Microsoft軟件，用起來很方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0404f4ef9d6cb71eca9093439265219af6a2cd1f","tid":2426743,"uid":14455,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T10:16:54.000Z","msg":"但係佢用iphone先玩到clubhouse<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc9ede284499b551427f4384a648c083ffa08f6d","tid":2426743,"uid":22832,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T10:32:48.000Z","msg":"個套lupin咁On9都睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a965a225e16b7ac2af4487172fa8243c6c8311a","tid":2426743,"uid":9387,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T10:35:23.000Z","msg":"死廢老bill gate用android岩架喇<br />\niphone留番俾我地連登精英用"},{"pid":"dd0d98ca1f270478c700b4adba941c869ff2dc71","tid":2426743,"uid":653,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T11:13:39.000Z","msg":"windows mobile呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71656ea2420332b7174cb357525f318f8d116c2e","tid":2426743,"uid":37097,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"dd0d98ca1f270478c700b4adba941c869ff2dc71","tid":2426743,"uid":653,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T11:13:39.000Z","msg":"windows mobile呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T11:17:10.000Z","msg":"唔係講笑, wm 個outlook 仲好用過ios/android<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b66d547d771ef572da6dbaaf116d6baccae33168","tid":2426743,"uid":653,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"71656ea2420332b7174cb357525f318f8d116c2e","tid":2426743,"uid":37097,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"dd0d98ca1f270478c700b4adba941c869ff2dc71","tid":2426743,"uid":653,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T11:13:39.000Z","msg":"windows mobile呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T11:17:10.000Z","msg":"唔係講笑, wm 個outlook 仲好用過ios/android<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T11:18:34.000Z","msg":"太小其他APPS<br />\n幾年前D WM撚係咁叫馬會出apps<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34247afbf985bef479efb5c2895a68a5bd416a68","tid":2426743,"uid":37097,"lik